@startuml C4_L1_System_Context
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 15
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam titleFontSize 22
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #333333
  BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
}
skinparam database {
  BorderColor #333333
  BackgroundColor #FFF4CC
}

title C4 Level 1 - System Context\nTicketing Microservices System

actor "Customer / User" as User
actor "Admin / Staff" as Admin

rectangle "Ticketing Microservices System" as System {
  rectangle "API Gateway" as Gateway
  rectangle "Ticketing Backend Services" as Backend
}

database "Service Databases\nH2 + Flyway migrations" as DB

User --> Gateway : uses ticketing API
Admin --> Gateway : manages events / inventory
Gateway --> Backend : routes REST requests
Backend --> DB : stores domain data

note right of System
Main features:
- Customer management
- Event management
- Ticket inventory management
- Ticket order management
end note

note bottom of Gateway
Single public entry point for API calls.
Routes requests to the correct backend service.
end note
@enduml
